
# Catery ☕

A single-page cafe website — "Savor the Pause, Love the Brew."

## Tech Stack

- TanStack Start / Router
- React + TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS

## Features

- Sticky header with smooth-scroll navigation (Home, Specials, Menu, About)
- Hero section with animated SVG coffee cup illustration
- Daily specials highlight
- Product menu carousel (click → to cycle items)
- About Us section with two cafe locations
- Contact modal (popup form) triggered from header, hero, and footer
- Fully responsive (mobile menu included)
- No external images — all visuals are custom inline SVG

## Getting Started

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open the app in your browser at the local dev URL shown in the terminal.

## Project Structure

- `routes/index.tsx` — main Catery landing page
- `routes/__root.tsx` — root layout, meta tags, error/404 handling
- `styles.css` — global styles

## Notes

All colors, fonts, and icons are self-contained in `index.tsx` — no external image or icon library required.
